edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configuration
Class ReadbackFPGA

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configuration.FPGA
      edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configuration.ReadbackFPGA

public class ReadbackFPGA
extends FPGA

Generates a configured FPGA object from a readback file. Since a readback bitstream does not have any of the packet information, we cannot use the bitstream parser to parser the bitstream into a data structure.
